mark":"Loss BOR 13/3 same prices both ends PnL -77,315 USD / TCE -1,106 USD"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-04-03T07:50:04.497","modifiedByFull":"Heng, Rainer","remark":"Redelivered vessel earlier on 09 Mar /0001h as no available cargo/voyage was found. Captured on VMS system completed date showing 13 Mar/0001H  for Pool cost and FHS."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-03-06T14:25:08.533","modifiedByFull":"Heng, Rainer","remark":"Updated with estimate redelivery date/time to owner and estimate Bunker ROB"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-24T23:33:05.783","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Difference:\u00A0\u00A0 A few differences here in this voyage that caused us to extend by about 2 weeks and end with the same profit.\u00A0 Vessel took 2 days longer to clean than estimated so tendered NOR right before laycan expired.\u00A0 Unfortunately, there were palms residues in one tank that caused first foot samples to fail.\u00A0 Skuld working the case with us and ultimately looks like Shell\u0027s position is strong to withhold laytime while we pumped the cargo back ashore and prepared again for balance loading (approx 3.5 days in discussion) so there is $160k exposure reflected in this result.\u00A0 Next will be to present that exposure as damages back to the owner for cleaning failure.\u00A0 Vessel took 6.5 days at Panama (booking split 50/50) but racked up 4.5 days on dems ($45k/day) adding $206k to result.\u00A0 Loading/discharging still took 7 days so able to add another $160k to result (factoring in the reservation).\u00A0 Bunker cost less than estimated despite extended voyage as LSGO price was less than estimated.\u00A0 ($950/mt vs $1294/mt est) and also VLSFO consumption very good compared to VMS estimate. (17 mt/day vs 22mt/day est)\u00A0 Overall of the 11 extra port days, 2 extra cleaning prior NOR, 3 lost due to poor cleaning, 1 for vessel\u0027s first COC (all on Stena account as per TCP) and 1 for bunkering outbound LA before ballasting across to FEAST all add time with no compensation."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-23T00:45:46.813","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"canal waiting added and demurrage updated (COC waiting time on our account unfo)"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-21T14:41:09.54","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"waiting for bunkers LA on our account"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-17T01:25:21.243","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Ets LA updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-16T21:22:23.413","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"laden bunkers panama-LA less than expected"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-16T15:35:42.89","modifiedByFull":"Petrusson, Rikard","remark":"Added the exposure of 160k for the ongoing claim with Shell and Head-Owners (OFF Spec cargo / time lost due to extra cleaning). TCE - 3434 / 160k PnL"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-08T03:46:59.043","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"bunkers at canal updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-01-31T10:17:36.04","modifiedByFull":"Petrusson, Rikard","remark":"Added extra demurrage for waiting time for transit in Panama. PnL \u002B 9063  / TCE -5736 USD"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-01-18T16:21:19.537","modifiedByFull":"Petrusson, Rikard","remark":"For IC: TC Chems overboard during passage from Ams to Panama (occurred 16th Jan but Stena Bulk informed 18th Jan..). Bad weather condition and poor lashing causing spillage of 9 drums in total (CC Alkaline and CC Neutral). Head-Owners are to pay for new chems in Panama. Note both chemicals are biodegradable and not causing any harm in the water."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-01-11T12:35:43.94","modifiedByFull":"Petrusson, Rikard","remark":"Added 3.5 in est demurrage and updated timings in Amsterdam. Note for IC: \u0022Off Spec\u0022 1st foot cargo (Carbob) Flushed and tested in each tank - downgraded into another tank ashore. Shell put Stena on Notice and we have put Head-Owners on notice. Skuld and P\u0026I surveyor to assist with this claim / TBC"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-12-30T03:03:01.413","modifiedByFull":"Rauston, Gustav","remark":"Bunker stem inserted into 2205"}],"offhireList":[{"id":193786,"dateStartUtc":null,"dateEndUtc":null,"days":null,"displayOrder":0,"offhireReason":null,"remark":null,"offhireBunkerList":[{"id":143417,"gradeName":"LSBF","quantity":null,"price":null,"displayOrder":0}]}],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}